---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="Our Process" 
    description="Understand the step-by-step process of dispute resolution at Aasra Arbitrix Mediation Hub LLP from filing a case to resolution."
>
    <HeroSection 
        title="The Dispute Resolution Process" 
        subtitle="A clear, structured approach to finding resolution" 
        showButton={false}
    />
    
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="process-intro">
                <p>At Aasra Arbitrix, we follow a systematic approach to dispute resolution that ensures fairness, efficiency, and satisfaction for all parties involved. Our structured process is designed to guide you from initial consultation to final resolution with clarity and support at every step.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="process-flow">
                <div class="process-step">
                    <div class="step-number">1</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Initial Consultation</h3>
                        <p>Begin with a preliminary meeting where we understand the nature of your dispute, explain our services, and determine the most appropriate resolution method for your situation.</p>
                        <div class="step-details">
                            <h4>What happens at this stage:</h4>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Discussing the dispute in detail</li>
                                <li>Exploring resolution options</li>
                                <li>Explaining the process and fees</li>
                                <li>Answering your questions and concerns</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="process-step">
                    <div class="step-number">2</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Case Filing and Documentation</h3>
                        <p>Submit your case through our formal filing process, providing all relevant documentation and information necessary for our mediators or arbitrators to understand the dispute fully.</p>
                        <div class="step-details">
                            <h4>What happens at this stage:</h4>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Completing the case intake form</li>
                                <li>Submitting relevant documents and evidence</li>
                                <li>Paying the initial fee</li>
                                <li>Receiving case confirmation and reference number</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="process-step">
                    <div class="step-number">3</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Panel Review and Assignment</h3>
                        <p>Our panel of experts reviews your case and assigns the most suitable mediator or arbitrator based on the specific nature and requirements of your dispute.</p>
                        <div class="step-details">
                            <h4>What happens at this stage:</h4>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Case assessment by our panel</li>
                                <li>Selection of appropriate resolution expert</li>
                                <li>Preliminary case evaluation</li>
                                <li>Scheduling of initial session</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="process-step">
                    <div class="step-number">4</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Mediation/Arbitration Sessions</h3>
                        <p>Participate in structured sessions facilitated by our experts, where all parties present their perspectives, discuss issues, and work toward resolution.</p>
                        <div class="step-details">
                            <h4>What happens at this stage:</h4>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Opening statements and issue identification</li>
                                <li>Facilitated discussion and negotiation</li>
                                <li>Exploration of possible solutions</li>
                                <li>In arbitration: evidence presentation and arguments</li>
                            </ul>
                            
                            <div class="process-note">
                                <strong>Note:</strong> The number and duration of sessions vary depending on the complexity of the case and the chosen resolution method.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="process-step">
                    <div class="step-number">5</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Agreement/Award Drafting</h3>
                        <p>Once a resolution is reached, our experts document the terms of the agreement (in mediation) or prepare a formal award (in arbitration) that clearly outlines the resolution.</p>
                        <div class="step-details">
                            <h4>What happens at this stage:</h4>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Drafting of comprehensive agreement/award</li>
                                <li>Review by all parties (in mediation)</li>
                                <li>Finalization of terms</li>
                                <li>Legal verification of the document</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="process-step">
                    <div class="step-number">6</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Resolution and Closure</h3>
                        <p>The final stage involves formalizing the agreement, implementing the resolution terms, and closing the case with follow-up support as needed.</p>
                        <div class="step-details">
                            <h4>What happens at this stage:</h4>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Signing of the final agreement</li>
                                <li>Implementation planning (if applicable)</li>
                                <li>Case closure documentation</li>
                                <li>Follow-up support (30 days)</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="section timeline-section" style="background-color: var(--neutral-100);">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Typical Timeline</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">While every case is unique, here's an approximate timeline for our dispute resolution process</p>
            
            <div class="timeline">
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <h3>Initial Consultation</h3>
                        <p class="timeline-duration">Day 1</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <h3>Case Filing & Documentation</h3>
                        <p class="timeline-duration">Days 2-7</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <h3>Panel Review & Assignment</h3>
                        <p class="timeline-duration">Days 8-14</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <h3>Mediation/Arbitration Sessions</h3>
                        <p class="timeline-duration">Days 15-45</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <h3>Agreement/Award Drafting</h3>
                        <p class="timeline-duration">Days 46-55</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <h3>Resolution & Closure</h3>
                        <p class="timeline-duration">Days 56-60</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <p class="timeline-note">* This timeline represents an average case. Simple disputes may be resolved in as little as 30 days, while complex cases may require 90+ days.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="section preparation-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">How to Prepare</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">Being well-prepared helps achieve an efficient and satisfactory resolution</p>
            
            <div class="preparation-grid">
                <div class="preparation-card">
                    <h3>Gather Documentation</h3>
                    <p>Collect all relevant documents related to your dispute, including contracts, correspondence, financial records, photographs, and any other evidence that supports your position.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="preparation-card">
                    <h3>Clarify Your Objectives</h3>
                    <p>Take time to identify what you hope to achieve through the resolution process. Consider your interests, needs, and priorities, as well as your best alternative if an agreement isn't reached.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="preparation-card">
                    <h3>Prepare Your Narrative</h3>
                    <p>Develop a clear, concise summary of the dispute from your perspective, focusing on key facts and issues rather than emotions or accusations.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="preparation-card">
                    <h3>Consider Possible Solutions</h3>
                    <p>Think about potential resolutions that might satisfy both your needs and the other party's. Being open to creative solutions often leads to more satisfactory outcomes.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="section cta-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="cta-content">
                <h2>Ready to Begin the Resolution Process?</h2>
                <p>Take the first step toward resolving your dispute by filing a case or contacting us today.</p>
                <div class="cta-buttons">
                    <a href="/file-case" class="btn btn-accent">File a Case</a>
                    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Us</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>

<style>
    .process-intro {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto var(--spacing-xxl);
        text-align: center;
    }
    
    .process-flow {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .process-step {
        display: flex;
        margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
    }
    
    .step-number {
        background-color: var(--primary-blue);
        color: white;
        width: 50px;
        height: 50px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        flex-shrink: 0;
        margin-right: var(--spacing-lg);
        margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .step-content {
        flex: 1;
    }
    
    .step-content h3 {
        color: var(--primary-blue);
        margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    }
    
    .step-details {
        background-color: var(--neutral-100);
        padding: var(--spacing-md);
        border-radius: var(--border-radius);
        margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
    }
    
    .step-details h4 {
        margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    
    .process-note {
        margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
        padding: var(--spacing-sm) var(--spacing-md);
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-red);
        border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    }
    
    .timeline {
        position: relative;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: var(--spacing-xl) auto 0;
    }
    
    .timeline::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        width: 4px;
        background-color: var(--primary-blue);
        left: 16px;
    }
    
    .timeline-item {
        position: relative;
        padding-left: 50px;
        margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
    }
    
    .timeline-marker {
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        width: 36px;
        height: 36px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background-color: white;
        border: 4px solid var(--primary-blue);
        top: 0;
    }
    
    .timeline-content {
        background-color: white;
        padding: var(--spacing-md);
        border-radius: var(--border-radius);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }
    
    .timeline-content h3 {
        margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
        color: var(--primary-blue);
    }
    
    .timeline-duration {
        color: var(--accent-red);
        font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    .timeline-note {
        text-align: center;
        color: var(--neutral-600);
        margin-top: var(--spacing-lg);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    
    .preparation-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: var(--spacing-lg);
        margin-top: var(--spacing-xl);
    }
    
    .preparation-card {
        background-color: white;
        padding: var(--spacing-lg);
        border-radius: var(--border-radius);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }
    
    .preparation-card h3 {
        color: var(--primary-blue);
        margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    }
    
    .cta-section {
        background-color: var(--primary-blue);
        color: white;
    }
    
    .cta-content {
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .cta-content h2 {
        color: white;
    }
    
    .cta-buttons {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: var(--spacing-md);
        margin-top: var(--spacing-lg);
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .process-step {
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        
        .step-number {
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
        }
        
        .timeline::before {
            left: 19px;
        }
        
        .preparation-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
        
        .cta-buttons {
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: var(--spacing-sm);
        }
    }
</style>